mer service phone number, eSignGlobal human customer service","176a165c-173a-8fbe":"eSignGlobal provides users with full-time online customer service telephone and human contact information, welcoming your inquiries.","6552c7c6-3f38-8b08":"eSignGlobal - A Global Leader in Electronic Signature Services","6e9ccc7d-3158-45d4":"With its market-leading position, global coverage, integrated solutions, localized services, and rich experience, eSignGlobal's global signing service solutions can effectively help enterprises achieve convenient, efficient, and compliant electronic signature services worldwide, enhancing business efficiency and competitiveness.","d91c5a82-e6da-b2a5":"Electronic Signature Leader","e147d5b7-e3ac-62c9":"eSignGlobal is a global electronic signature technology service provider. As of now, eSignGlobal's operational data has consistently ranked first in the industry. eSignGlobal has participated in the formulation of 5 standards and is the only electronic signature company to have been included in the Hurun Global Unicorn List for 5 consecutive years.","ce44bb3d-f823-3551":"Infrastructure Builder","1388f6f7-d525-61e0":"Designated electronic signature service provider for 10+ Chinese provincial governments, serving 100+ Fortune Global 500 companies, 200+ China Fortune 500 companies, 150+ Chinese provincial/municipal government clients, with 1500+ scenario applications and 3000+ ecosystem partners deeply integrated.","26bba76a-bca7-bf71":"The Most Comprehensive Qualification Internet Electronic Signature Company","4acb11c7-c440-57ef":"eSignGlobal is a member of organizations such as the China National Cryptography Standardization Technical Committee, the Information Technology Application Innovation Working Committee of the China Electronics Standardization Association, the China Electronic Chamber of Commerce Autonomous and Controllable Technology Committee, and the CSA Global Cloud Security Alliance, participating in the formulation of multiple Chinese national and local industry standards.","ae735e31-4877-a3e2":"eSignGlobal's professional, authoritative, and reliable business experience supports industry development. With industry-core qualifications, eSignGlobal gains greater recognition from the judicial system.","894301e2-04ca-69f0":"The China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission is one of the major permanent commercial arbitration institutions in the world.","654ed85c-6948-001c":"As of 2023, the CIETAC has handled over 60,000 arbitration cases worldwide, involving parties from more than 160 countries and regions.","783f649a-8950-7014":"CIETAC is a long-term cooperative partner of eSignGlobal and recognizes the validity of evidence generated by eSignGlobal's overseas signing services.","a2032f16-663b-7a6d":"How to use eSignGlobal overseas signing evidence to apply for international arbitration?","e0647bbb-eeee-052a":"· Add an arbitration clause to commercial business contracts.","efcfaf67-6203-b19e":"· Any disputes arising from or related to this contract shall be submitted to the China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission (CIETAC) for arbitration in accordance with the effective arbitration rules of CIETAC at the time of applying for arbitration. The arbitration award is final and binding on both parties.","6e203dec-2518-1258":"· Collect the signed contract, signing completion certificate, and other relevant evidence materials, and submit an arbitration application.","23994ed8-cd31-8880":"· CIETAC will select and initiate the general, simplified, or domestic arbitration procedure based on the case circumstances.","8da17b4b-04e0-5d94":"· The arbitration award will be signed and delivered, and the parties shall execute or immediately enforce the judgment according to the deadline.","a04d2797-030b-bde4":"· If a party fails to enforce by the deadline, apply to the court for mandatory enforcement.","be5669df-667a-39e0":"Full Coverage, Meeting GlobalDemands","3d57f68c-9057-91fe":"· Support for 100+ countries and regions: eSignGlobal supports electronic signature services in over 100 countries and regions, meeting compliance requirements in different areas.","9b90b1eb-8f15-bef5":"· Multiple signing modes: Supports local-overseas, overseas-overseas, overseas-local, and other signing modes to flexibly meet the needs of different scenarios.","bfee2c4c-2ae1-c7f1":"Industry-Leading Security System","288745df-58be-bf46":"Top-tier Service Performance In the Industry","9105cb10-801a-f9f6":"Global Multi-Data Center","1c36f5f6-79a7-6c1b":"· Hong Kong, Singapore, European Union multi-data centers: Meeting compliance requirements of various countries.","055f33af-198c-b5eb":"· Integration with iAM Smart: Offers AES-level signatures and supports QES-level signatures for mainland China.","f57f4431-b78b-dafa":"· Hong Kong local service team: Provides convenient and efficient localized service support.","b492b32d-6f97-5152":"Successful Cases  Rich Experience","fed188f9-ef42-475d":"· eSignGlobal has numerous successful cases covering industries such as human resources, transportation, engineering construction, overseas e-commerce, 3D software services, new energy materials, international communications, cultural media, and art transactions, accumulating rich experience and providing customized solutions for clients.","ceaef4d2-3299-14db":"· eSignGlobal has deeply integrated with many ecosystem partners, creating the most comprehensive industry ecosystem network in the industry, with over 3000 partners, launching numerous integrated products. It can be quickly launched with simple configuration, reducing the cost of user informatization system construction.","f1ad2535-70b2-583b":"Choose eSignGlobal","2c484f47-6e50-c90c":"Convenient, efficient, secure, low-cost, and eco-friendly","9dd86595-a0a1-e403":"Choose eSignGlobal","c3f6dec8-a9a5-fe87":"Convenient, efficient, secure, low-cost, and eco-friendly","95ba2de2-1370-7bcd":"Industry Pain Points","5ab9d65d-7c95-cd10":"Application Scenarios","5432c88a-5335-551e":"Solutions","9189aeb0-ec3b-abd4":"Customer Cases","74b71645-05b7-1583":"Industry Pain Points","8e012127-0d8c-7c01":"Low Efficiency","fca519f4-7cce-7abd":"Long cycle for paper contract signing, complicated process for remote signing, up to 15 days.","2b13335c-a74e-cd7d":"High Cost","0a41b2c3-f6a1-a4c2":"A series of costs associated with paper contracts: such as paper cost, printing cost, courier cost, storage cost, personnel cost, etc.","d15b9b0b-1781-123e":"Difficult Management","6b21eae5-02e1-315d":"Large amount of labor required for the storage and archiving of paper contracts, and extensive workload for future review and auditing.","f938086e-4740-dce2":"High Risk","2a7fd862-a026-c905":"Physical seals are difficult to authenticate, paper contracts are easy to alter, posing a high risk.","33c308ed-f298-65a9":"Application Scenarios","57ccb5d0-a3e4-79f7":"Property Management","478ed50a-c43e-3b6b":"Property service agreements, other daily documents","d21f2651-0019-0669":"Housing Lease","dd5c42d3-8984-2087":"Housing lease contract, housing entrustment contract","28c96c99-f36b-ff13":"Human Resources Management","b00aab64-908a-4ffd":"Labor contracts, HR-related certificates","44207d9a-43ac-7ed0":"Internal Approval","4fdc752f-a3a6-bb82":"Purchase contracts, supplier framework contracts, delivery agreements","9a5ee3d8-e2bc-9e9c":"Solutions","9218f30b-9d2a-2475":"Human Resources Management Electronic Signature Application","d6649952-91e8-9d38":"Lease Agreement Electronic Signature Application","e627d5be-8033-13a4":"Purchase Contract Signing","c1e874ac-80b5-f5ea":"Follow-on Investment Agreement","ef8c7623-70fa-89bc":"Scene Introduction","fe57ff3f-d2ef-3f98":"Real estate companies have branches all over the country, often involving the problem of remote signing of a large number of labor contracts and other documents, which needs to be addressed urgently. The signing parties involved in the human resources applications within the company mainly include employers and employees.","5b7fe0b1-0971-8218":"Scene Introduction","fae550b0-caeb-4458":"As real estate companies develop, they gradually transition from business transactions to leasing, covering both C-end and B-end, and leading companies are all moving towards online platforms. This transition requires process onlineization, and electronic signatures are an indispensable part of it.","a7cfd376-8002-be4c":"Applicable Scenarios","e187410a-2719-383e":"Enterprise purchase contract signing can be integrated with internal OA, ERP, SAP, and other systems to enable electronic signature functionality, allowing external suppliers to sign documents on terminal devices or within the procurement system.","dc08fd14-99b5-c72c":"Process Introduction","24e300f8-9e9c-fe1b":"The electronic signature system can be integrated with the company's related business systems. After integration, the signing personnel can sign through various methods such as website portals, SMS, and email (requires identity authentication) to achieve full-process digitization.","22e2c8e5-639c-8e89":"Scene Introduction","4f1ceb0b-0dc0-1b19":"Employees within the real estate company can make follow-on investments in the company's internal subscription system, and the electronic seal function is integrated into the company's subscription system. Employees log in to the APP to complete the online subscription and signing.","e2292df4-da88-5520":"Customer Cases","1cc00ec9-610d-1233":"More Customer Cases","abd2d4e4-409d-efd0":"Industry Pain Points","71477a5a-ccff-63a1":"Application Scenarios","62fcd731-0cfb-b04e":"Solutions","766a9894-bb3b-ec63":"Customer Cases","60d0442a-f61f-e063":"Industry Pain Points","d8446eab-c4f0-00af":"Complex Account Opening Process","99e6338f-1335-3e66":"Requires customers to fill out a large number of forms and visit branches for identity verification and signature sealing, which is time-consuming and labor-intensive, affecting customer experience.","862d33e1-3e91-b507":"Difficulty in Acquiring Out-of-Town Customers","1129be1e-19d6-78b3":"High Cost of Paper Contract F2F: The cost of face-to-face signing with clients is high, as client managers need to visit multiple times, leading to increased costs.","bc9df8c2-88d8-d1a7":"Difficulty in File Management","0cfedacf-7d69-f054":"Business contracts are numerous, and the storage of paper contracts occupies space. It is inconvenient to search and manage, and it is easy to lose or damage.","98d94f92-5568-9645":"Insufficient Security","7b596036-0743-419e":"Easily Altered: Paper contracts are easily altered, making it difficult to ensure the authenticity of the contract content.","b9c1bdf2-42bc-87b5":"Easily Lost: Paper contracts are easily lost or damaged, leading to the loss of important information.","fffc54dd-785c-f5de":"Insufficient Evidential Effectiveness:","825cda7e-3aa3-3d9b":"As evidence, paper contracts have certain risks of effectiveness, making it difficult to effectively protect their own rights and interests.","347430ac-d338-fa49":"Application Scenarios","0ef58350-6c93-b7e6":"Credit and Financial Management Services","1e715abf-b302-3389":"Electronic signatures streamline online credit and finance services for banks, digitizing traditional processes.","36531671-67f1-59ec":"Internal Office Work","86a32b99-a55b-bb6b":"Bank operations and management include various approval processes that require identity authentication for applicants and approvers to ensure proper authorization and accountability.","49ad952e-2fa8-d023":"Fund Financing Business","a7e6203b-412b-c01d":"Fund financing agreements require customers and securities companies to sign and seal, and submit related materials, with a complex and time-consuming process.","8be7c114-49f6-3c9d":"Insurance Application, Claims, and Policy Management","952da365-d71f-ef77":"Customers fill out paper applications, agents submit them, and customers manage policies and claims through an app, which the company processes.","cf248187-165d-e49f":"Solutions","29717e69-d4c5-12b0":"Credit and Financial Management Services","09a8a237-a5bb-2e34":"Internal Office Work","c044ff8f-817a-265b":"Counter Paperless","b2355eb4-43c2-cad9":"Applicable Scenarios","4eeba05a-9ee5-eb96":"Personal/Micro Small and Medium Enterprise Loans, signing credit authorization letters and loan contracts","ec9345a1-dfef-6831":"Process Introduction","ebc809db-a025-70c8":"1. Users perform identity verification within the bank's system.","9b375164-0fbe-41c7":"2. Users authorize credit checks, sign the credit authorization agreement, the bank conducts credit extension, and returns the credit limit.","8551311b-59c7-e2e2":"3. Users sign the loan agreement, eSignGlobal provides electronic signature services, once the user signs, the bank automatically signs, and the contract becomes effective.","f152b966-e5e1-7c6d":"4. eSignGlobal provides evidence preservation services, which can store evidence of the signing process, and offer certification services subsequently.","1c985e30-6896-00ce":"Applicable Scenarios","c6dc1b58-b704-a87a":"The bank's operations and management activities involve approval and stamping business processes.","0b9fa3c4-a91c-12d2":"Process Introduction","1c76ee98-c528-9fec":"Internal employees log in to the OA system, initiate the seal approval, and after approval, enter the electronic signature management page. Through the bank's seal management system, complete operations such as specifying the signature location, previewing the signature file, controlling printing permissions, and adding digital watermarks, and finally automatically archive the electronic files.","d880a412-ca03-345c":"Applicable Scenarios","d05dde4e-c6b2-9a5b":"Operational and management activities involving approval, stamping, and printing in bank operations","5b264bf1-1459-670d":"Process Introduction","82070a28-13c2-1c80":"Internal employees log in to the OA system, initiate the seal approval, and after approval, enter the electronic signature management page. Through the bank's seal management system, complete operations such as specifying the signature location, previewing the signature file, controlling printing permissions, and adding digital watermarks, and finally automatically archive the electronic files.","f22c0685-bfe6-8dea":"Customer Cases","6cdc26c5-2f01-43d6":"Industry Pain Points","28665865-6ea7-ad57":"Application Scenarios","239c36f4-5ae2-36d4":"Solutions","56c6292d-d77b-ccab":"Customer Cases","342c3e23-054f-d54f":"Industry Pain Points","0ecd513f-199d-48b9":"Ensuring the Authenticity of Online Digital Identity","270e7298-c6d6-6179":"The ‘Internet+’ government services system enables online business handling without physical presence, ensuring the authenticity and reliability of the user’s identity.","e26b04f6-1366-d88a":"Ensuring the Authenticity and Reliability of Online Business","2c1f4830-429c-1d3f":"After achieving paperless business processing, how to ensure the authenticity and reliability of business data.","4583fc50-c375-18c0":"Legality of Electronic Data","32981613-ca91-3b16":"For data that is prone to legal disputes, how to ensure that relevant data can quickly prove its legal effectiveness in case of disputes.","edd3f6d8-981c-3f96":"Diversity of Electronic Signature Methods","6c1c309b-c2be-dadd":"Need to provide different electronic signature methods to enable legal entities and natural persons to use them conveniently and quickly.","ffd329a1-9daa-e7af":"Application Scenarios","9af3a016-d5ec-5c03":"Government Affairs Network","6bd4a579-b59b-99c1":"Document circulation and administrative approval within the government intranet environment require seal and stamping.","df470acb-ab37-2a09":"Electronic Signature","4f5f2005-5d5d-e2bb":"Government services websites, business and individual services, electronic certificates all require stamping and sealing.","823427bb-f3f2-da2e":"Business Systems","6f7fbdb8-e5d3-ed2b":"Batch processing and stamping of electronic certificates and other documents","ae070bc3-c181-9f03":"Solutions","a4a77714-ab76-af07":"Government Internal Document Circulation","408b0310-c7fe-886c":"Government Agency Electronic Certificate Application","006c5f4c-9bf2-c3f7":"On-Site Business Processing","02293b55-ce2f-86a5":"Applicable Scenarios","ad81a333-7db9-7aa5":"Before sending electronic documents to the recipient, they need to be stamped with the official seal of the sending party. If it is a joint issuance, the official seals of the relevant parties involved in the joint issuance are also needed. Additionally, for electronic documents, it is necessary to archive both the paper and electronic contracts.","219290ee-9fda-414a":"Process Introduction","0525bd3a-27c5-af1f":"The particularity of electronic documents lies in their seriousness and confidentiality. After the entire signing process is completed, it is also necessary to print and save them, and set the printing control times. Often, a QR code is attached to the paper document to facilitate understanding of the related electronic document.","347d21e1-3ba4-3b77":"Scene Introduction","27519e7f-4e55-161f":"With the development of society, the security and anti-counterfeiting ability of ID photos have greatly reduced, and the continuous occurrence of fake IDs has also brought a significant impact. Therefore, it is urgent to promote the online application of electronic certificates for administrative approval services and to carry out the full process of electronic work at all levels of administrative organs.","b4511c2b-2d3c-9427":"Process Introduction","75d508ad-8d55-1f04":"Through the interface, collect metadata of certificates from the business system or electronic certificate repository, generate the formatted file of the electronic certificate using the certificate template, and then apply electronic signatures and timestamps to the formatted file to form the electronic file of the electronic certificate.","1fca96bd-2315-4267":"Applicable Scenarios","e837ea24-e84e-434c":"After the construction of the government services website, it is recommended that users complete the online processing in principle. However, due to various reasons, some businesses need to be processed at the service hall. Traditional on-site processing requires carrying a large number of paper materials, which is not conducive to environmental protection, and a large number of paper materials need to be archived, which is not conducive to management. Therefore, on-site processing also needs to be paperless.","bc73068c-40e4-c247":"Process Introduction","2dd6cba9-e339-4e71":"Relevant personnel need to complete the filling of related matters online and perform online signatures. After that, they go to the service hall in person, where the staff match the identity through authentication. After confirmation, both parties perform the stamping action to obtain the service receipt.","9cd187cc-10e9-7120":"Customer Cases","eeb84884-f60b-03c8":"More Customer Cases","3248a23b-cc37-1bd8":"Industry Pain Points","b20d3429-7c3f-6051":"Application Scenarios","615ae7cd-d04d-dd80":"Solutions","4ee39895-a9f0-f259":"Customer Cases","3967ec5e-fd5d-c36e":"Industry Pain Points","a46ec8f2-406b-fe72":"Storage Security","24ccf7ce-1bf2-7d5d":"Paper contracts are susceptible to natural disasters such as fire and water damage, and cannot completely avoid the risk of theft or tampering.","8ffaaf3c-2527-a5f5":"Low Efficiency","75b5fd12-2c68-bf80":"Cross-regional and cross-departmental stamping needs take a long time, resulting in low efficiency.","4ad2a853-9db0-b3f7":"High Cost","6b7dd3ad-f819-fc4c":"The process of document signing involves a large amount of paper and postal costs, and the management costs are enormous.","a9ab4e70-e009-829e":"Varied Application Scenarios","f5a7c226-912b-e505":"Often a large group will have many demand scenarios, requiring targeted solutions for different scenarios.","b86f04a6-d224-93ac":"Application Scenarios","e6c240de-a146-5126":"Supply Chain System","096714f3-5c78-007a":"B2B business contracts, logistics-related contracts and documents, supply chain finance-related agreements, etc.","8a27f07d-0ff0-6eb5":"Purchasing Platform System","b4b36eab-c7f7-daa3":"Purchasing contracts, reconciliation statements, and other related documents","05999730-f0b7-4de3":"HR System","f315d08d-e476-9f63":"Contracts and internal proof materials","075a6862-1f19-280a":"Solutions","78f5e181-7121-7937":"Proof Document Signing","6105ead7-fd03-a241":"Labor Contract Signing","5453dca4-7dd9-1844":"Business Contract Signing","298cc6bc-878d-a2d4":"Scene Introduction","d8020798-9b02-fa3f":"Manufacturing enterprises inevitably require a large workforce for production, and with a high turnover of employees, there is a frequent need for related proofs and documents. To simplify employee operations and improve efficiency, enterprises use electronic seals to address this issue.","bb16b9fc-59eb-dd26":"Process Introduction","b7df0f24-c413-b618":"Employees apply for materials through the enterprise's internal system (such as the HR system). After the application is approved, the enterprise internally can choose silent signing or a dedicated seal officer to stamp different materials. After completion, they are given to the employees.","5668f0db-30b6-c140":"Scene Introduction","4681e199-77fe-8b14":"Manufacturing companies often have a large number of employees, and many large enterprises are spread across the country and even the world. Signing labor contracts is a very big problem, and due to the employees being a vulnerable group, the signing of such contracts requires more attention to privacy and legal effectiveness.","c82f45cc-8599-509c":"Process Introduction","e7e7cabb-6af1-ada5":"Employees apply for materials through the enterprise's internal system (such as the HR system). After the application is approved, the enterprise internally can choose silent signing or a dedicated seal officer to stamp different materials. After completion, they are given to the employees for confirmation. HR enters relevant information in the relevant system (HR system), and through the template directly generates the contract document to be signed. After initiating the signing process, employees receive a signing link to complete the signing (identity authentication). The enterprise can choose to automatically sign before or after the employee signs. This completes the entire signing process.","9833060b-95d7-4995":"Scene Introduction","87b517bc-8f7f-8f6e":"In the daily work of manufacturing companies, there will be a large number of contract signings, including cooperation agreements and supply contracts with suppliers, and purchase contracts with distributors.","db2a5557-c5a4-0bac":"Customer Cases","b361841c-2bea-e54a":"More Customer Cases","e630c057-faa4-4e40":"Medical and Health Care Scenario","d5fc3df9-b293-fb5a":"Widely integrated digital infrastructure","0292f83f-dcfb-256d":"Function Introduction","95f83b02-4b81-e74d":"Product Advantages","87382390-5a20-d012":"Application Scenarios","c266fff4-3386-72ab":"Customer Cases","c325363b-f34f-b3dd":"Utilizing password technology, electronic signature, authentication, cloud computing, blockchain, AI, middleware, and multi-tenancy, this system establishes a regional, trusted health care signing network. It digitizes the medical industry, supporting various signing scenarios like medical staff and patient signatures, and administrative archiving, with potential for expansion into other health care areas.","2a85b84e-c98d-1b47":"Product Advantages","45bf9ac5-0e84-7728":"Create Core Technology Standards","3d115665-f970-0fac":"Create Core Technology Standards","0a4ce979-462e-24cb":"01. Compliant with multiple national standards for electronic signatures in the healthcare industry.","35c20d64-07dc-7c08":"02. Data sharding, multi-tenant isolation, distributed key segmentation encryption, original sandbox protection, and core technology support","129c7828-ef00-81f0":"Enable Rapid and Convenient Delivery","fab9cd74-a6b6-a7d9":"Enable Rapid and Convenient Delivery","c9ca4242-0b78-c1e4":"01. A single system provides comprehensive electronic authentication and signature services","4f577ec4-64c7-8613":"02. eSignGlobal open platform services with few interfaces and clear timing","836a0f75-22c6-cec7":"03. User system configuration is flexible, synchronized with a single click","65349704-b360-9e44":"Focus on Industry Application Details","fefabb2d-0b51-710e":"Focus on Industry Application Details","5bb4d25b-0834-d225":"01. Software functionality design based on clinical scenarios","0c569722-fb7f-e72d":"02. Supports personalized authentication modes at hospital, department, and individual levels","5bc3121e-96b2-0be8":"03. No need to install additional APPs","1d6c6206-dfbd-e721":"04. Focus on Legal Compliance Details","0c8a4e8d-5ce8-6d67":"Provide Comprehensive Service Assurance","07f110d6-9eb8-c647":"Provide Comprehensive Service Assurance","362e4791-c73d-9e00":"01. Provide full-process evidence preservation, evidence issuance, verification, and legal services","d8d8f2fe-2432-ac3a":"02. Seamless integration with Ant Chain and the Supreme People's Court judicial chain","0a4087ee-3968-1924":"03. Assist clients in jointly promoting medical electronic signature applications","840686e6-3c79-190f":"Application Scenarios","6e9d1862-c752-77fa":"Medical and Nursing Signatures","be15be87-e800-4b18":"Medical and Nursing Signatures mainly secure the circulation of various documents such as medical orders, medical records, examination reports, hospital admission records, imaging reports, and electronic prescriptions during the treatment process.","532053db-36dd-09b5":"Patient Signatures","200a9286-d05a-e8c8":"Patient Signatures mainly for signatures by patients and their families, including surgical consent forms, admission records, informed consent forms, patient authorization forms, and risk assessment tables.","564d92a1-9282-a6fc":"Archive Trusted Archival Management Signatures","baba6d5b-b799-a15b":"Archive Trusted Archival Management from various information systems within the hospital intranet collects medical data and packages it into a formatted document that is application-independent, non-repudiable, easy to read, and legally recognized.","bcb34bc8-ff70-d768":"Administrative Management Signatures","32f4ff50-c1fd-c2d5":"Administrative signatures are primarily used for the signing of documents within health administrative departments and medical institutions, such as daily office files, finance, legal documents, and approval processes.","03f1c041-c0b3-167a":"Customer Cases","d31323cc-cf3c-f449":"Healthcare Scenario","e670018d-cf5c-b855":"MediSign Electronic Authentication and Signature System - Widely integrated digital infrastructure","daa2b388-0a48-496b":"Based on password technology, electronic signatures, identity authentication, cloud computing, blockchain, AI, middleware technology, and multi-tenancy, it builds a trusted healthcare signing network covering the region for various health and health departments, empowering the digital transformation of the healthcare industry. It supports multiple typical signing scenarios within the scope of medical institution business: medical and nursing signatures, patient signatures, administrative management trusted archiving, etc., and supports expansion to other healthcare business scenarios.","f491751b-78f0-3a99":"Foundational Infrastructure for Security and Compliance","59192e8a-0c7c-5c6b":"Create Core Technology Standards","c8417beb-f495-9cf6":"01. Establish multiple national standards, industry standards, and local standards","a279cd6d-7168-45a5":"02. Data sharding, multi-tenant isolation, distributed key segmentation encryption, original sandbox protection, and core technology support","adb408fb-991f-bd5e":"Enable Rapid and Convenient Delivery","75641b6f-7858-f906":"01. A single system provides comprehensive electronic authentication and signature services","d3d95225-dab8-16ed":"02. eSignGlobal open platform services with few interfaces and clear timing","02055a6c-45b4-f77c":"03. User system configuration is flexible, synchronized with a single click","d566558c-4bba-6ac8":"Focus on Industry Application Details","18dc84ab-31fd-514e":"01. Software functionality design based on clinical scenarios","52ea79c7-0daf-45c1":"02. Supports personalized authentication modes at hospital, department, and individual levels","96f4ab34-5a1c-36c7":"03. No need to install additional APPs","7eae53e7-a005-764e":"04. Focus on Legal Compliance Details","d6e882e0-55da-0879":"Provide Comprehensive Service Assurance","c9b20709-3d0a-2c2c":"01. Provide full-process evidence preservation, evidence issuance, verification, and legal services","8cfb711f-4cc9-1fec":"02. Seamless integration with Ant Chain, the Supreme People's Court judicial chain","86d03508-b9fc-a2dc":"03. Assist clients in jointly promoting medical electronic signature applications","d557e956-ebc2-5aef":"Create Core Technology Standards","bb9f2550-8e27-c595":"01. Establish multiple national standards, industry standards, and local standards","29dc7085-cf15-98d7":"02. Data sharding, multi-tenant isolation, distributed key segmentation encryption, original sandbox protection, and core technology support","ad273727-cb0d-9551":"Enable Rapid and Convenient","a072cc3c-93a4-8103":"02. Support personalized authentication modes at hospital, department, and individual levels","a121754e-8281-6102":"03. No need to install additional APPs","4361ddc8-0858-98e8":"04. Focus on legal compliance details","5a0235ae-439a-cac3":"Provide comprehensive service assurance","e75a0a46-a8ed-8b52":"01. Provide full-process evidence preservation, evidence issuance, verification, and legal services","42058eba-aef4-5bfc":"02. Seamless integration with Ant Chain, the Supreme People's Court judicial chain","f6a8b0cc-4945-3373":"03. Assist clients in jointly promoting medical electronic signature applications","dc151800-cc58-65cd":"Create core technology standards","c79b01fa-827a-de4c":"01. Establish multiple national standards, industry standards, and local standards","0d725541-e432-9fa4":"02. Data sharding, multi-tenant isolation, distributed key segmentation encryption, original sandbox protection, and core technology support","227a55a1-cec2-6751":"Enable rapid and convenient delivery","f7c92ca9-0fc5-4c06":"01. A single system provides comprehensive electronic authentication and signature services","c78a69ff-4c0b-0427":"02. eSignGlobal open platform services with few interfaces and clear timing","dee5149b-253f-e122":"03. User system configuration is flexible, synchronized with a single click","533dd210-0402-7df0":"Focus on industry application details","642fc7f0-b86c-9266":"01. Software functionality design based on clinical scenarios","08f3cf50-5acf-d666":"02. Support personalized authentication modes at hospital, department, and individual levels","ee3105d3-51f3-57df":"03. No need to install additional APPs","663607ac-5edc-7d94":"04. Focus on legal compliance details","c11ffc4b-3423-3151":"Provide comprehensive service assurance","3a74458c-fc4e-3141":"01. Provide full-process evidence preservation, evidence issuance, verification, and legal services","646f83ac-15c5-6345":"02. Seamless integration with Ant Chain, the Supreme People's Court judicial chain","d7064cb4-d674-d494":"03. Assist clients in jointly promoting medical electronic signature applications","63abb07d-a702-2a10":"Healthcare scenario","3d525b1a-3b1b-5703":"Medical and nursing signatures","6d877931-8d4f-aa4e":"Medical and nursing signatures mainly for the secure circulation of various documents such as medical orders, medical records, examination reports, hospital admission records, imaging reports, and electronic prescription dispensing during the treatment process.","fa5ea4d3-d07a-bc0d":"Patient signatures","cb6bccdb-9acd-f3f0":"Patient signatures mainly for signatures by patients and their families, including surgical consent forms, admission records, informed consent forms, patient authorization forms, and risk assessment tables.","b7c5abb3-b63d-b5c0":"Archive trusted archival management signatures","ed39abd8-10b9-379f":"Management involves the collection and archivization encapsulation of medical data from a variety of information systems within the hospital’s internal network, resulting in a format that is application-independent, non-repudiable, easily readable, and legally valid.","b337b1fe-5f5f-b013":"Customer Cases","0e69fcb5-4e78-d10c":"Solution Advantages","e396589d-fcfe-2ead":"Solution Overview","bcce8bbe-8339-faa0":"Customer Cases","4bfcdf8c-1a7e-cb01":"Solution Advantages","4839b500-9c13-fea0":"Rich Product Solutions","aedcb646-6679-93db":"Offer flexible product solutions tailored to different customer types”","31fbd05a-ece6-b1fb":"Legally Binding Electronic Signatures","82cacee9-82f0-922c":"Adhere strictly to global electronic signature laws in process design, ensuring that the signed documents are fully legally binding.","d0867090-9fa9-ae54":"Excellent User Experience","d56d86c0-7a5b-c6ae":"Support multiple signing methods, including H5, Alipay, WeChat, and various real-name authentication services","5d0f8a83-b675-9469":"Evidence Preservation and Legal Services","a66fca44-9d14-01ac":"eSignGlobal provides third-party evidence reports, judicial appraisal reports, notarized documents, online arbitration, third-party mediation, legal consultation, and other legal services","77a781c0-98c2-3dea":"Solution Overview","56d5038a-ab7b-4ff6":"Labor Contracts/Resignation Agreements","ab73a012-d7b2-0ea9":"Proof Documents","3692f87e-d614-b10d":"Company Internal Confirmation Materials","6929b5eb-ddac-aa1f":"Solution Process:","b2a60fd3-df64-017e":"1. Employees handle their entry and exit procedures, HR personnel fill in the information in the office system and initiate the signing process;","9c7d5030-4615-2323":"2. Employees receive notification to review the contracts to be signed. If not authenticated, they need to perform real-name authentication first, then complete the signing after SMS intention authentication;","855627bb-64f5-e860":"3. After the employee signs, the signed document goes to the HR personnel, who check for accuracy and complete the signing;","1d200613-f540-ae44":"4. After signing, employees can view the signed contract in the HR system, and the contract signing information can be stored in eSignGlobal's open service.","56aacb8b-2aeb-4a57":"Solution Process:","f1f1cb6b-233b-d128":"1. Employees initiate the proof document process approval in the OA system;","dd960fe3-f0c5-a043":"2. HR confirms the content of the proof document, and internal managers review the business flow;","52abf746-f6d6-db8e":"3. After approval, the system calls eSignGlobal's electronic signature service to complete the electronic signing of the proof document.","53cfedac-0049-c4b0":"4. The business system displays the signed documents, which employees can view and download.","f89f03de-8798-591a":"Solution Process:","f6c8a14b-1551-113d":"1. HR personnel fill in the information in the office system, and internal reviewers confirm the employee's materials;","2d22eeb7-d3f3-af47":"2. After the materials are confirmed, HR initiates the internal material signing, and the enterprise stamps first, eSignGlobal synchronously notifies the employee;","5cebeecf-d911-9b15":"3. Employees receive signing notifications. If not authenticated, they need to perform real-name authentication first, then complete intention authentication, and confirm the signing;","6e2f18db-4022-c2f5":"4. After the employee signs, the signed document goes to the office system, and employees can view the signed contract in the HR system, with the contract signing information stored in eSignGlobal's open service.","6abb5c33-c7ab-20da":"Customer Cases","bb37da46-a309-6d09":"Geely Motors uses eSignGlobal electronic signature services in human resources scenarios, which not only facilitates employees but also improves the efficiency of the human resources department.","cceea658-7cea-0ea0":"Lanmei, after introducing eSignGlobal electronic signatures into their eHR system, HR can initiate the signing of labor contracts with employees at any time within the eHR system, effectively promoting cost reduction and efficiency increase through online signing.","c8a2d0c7-3ddd-bef2":"Roche Pharmaceuticals, a world-leading health care company, uses eSignGlobal electronic signature services in multiple scenarios such as personnel certification and electronic labor contracts, significantly improving service efficiency.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5411":"Shanghai New Vision - Human Resources","c2b5f03e-23f6-5412":"Overseas human resources service company, providing recruitment and labor outsourcing services, helping companies that need to go abroad recruit suitable talents.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5413":"Service provider signs the 'Labor Contract' with individuals in foreign countries, and branches in China/Singapore/other countries initiate the signing. Employees in foreign countries (Spain, Australia, etc.) receive signing notifications and complete contract signing online.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5414":"Using the overseas signing page to initiate and API interface to initiate contract signing","c2b5f03e-23f6-5415":"Connect to the human resources service platform, generate labor contract documents with one click","c2b5f03e-23f6-5416":"Overseas signatories can receive signing notifications and links via email, view and sign the documents.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5417":"Hong Kong Yutong International - Transportation","c2b5f03e-23f6-5418":"Yutong International has a vast domestic logistics network and a large number of car rental platforms, specializing in large and bulk goods transportation services both domestically and internationally, and is an authorized foreign trade company with national approval for import and export trade.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5419":"Online signing of 'Overseas Sales Contracts' with Hong Kong and global clients, achieving unified online signing and management of business contracts.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5421":"Phase 1 uses the overseas signing page to initiate, phase 2 considers integrating with the business system","c2b5f03e-23f6-5428":"Online initiation of sales contracts, global signing","c2b5f03e-23f6-5422":"Meet global electronic signature grade requirements and reduce contract signing costs","c2b5f03e-23f6-5423":"China Construction - Engineering Construction","c2b5f03e-23f6-5424":"The only subsidiary enterprise with headquarters both domestically and internationally, focusing on overseas business and integrating domestic and international development. It has implemented a series of overseas projects with significant influence, including the Pakistan PKM project (Sukkur-Multan section), the Egypt New Capital Central Business District (CBD) project, the Congo (Brazzaville) National Highway Franchise, the Sri Lanka Southern Expressway Extension, and the Israel Tel Aviv Green Line project, in line with the 'Belt and Road' initiative.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5425":"Human Resources, Procurement Supply, Financial Management, Sales, Strategic Cooperation, External Archives, etc.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5426":"Full-scene application integration","c2b5f03e-23f6-5427":"Fruugo - Overseas E-commerce","c2b5f03e-23f6-5429":"Fruugo is a European overseas e-commerce platform headquartered in the UK. Its business covers more than 200 countries and regions globally. On Fruugo, sellers can publish their products and sell them to global consumers.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5431":"Overseas e-commerce platforms initiate signing, Chinese merchants sign the 'Merchant Settlement Agreement' and cc the overseas e-commerce platform entity to ensure orderly cooperation between the overseas platform and merchants.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5432":"Solve the cooperation challenges between overseas e-commerce platforms and Chinese merchants.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5433":"Overseas initiation, domestic signing, merchant identity is authentic and credible.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5434":"The overseas platform collects and archives the cc after signing is completed.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5435":"United Solar Polysilicon (FZC) - New Energy Materials","c2b5f03e-23f6-5436":"Headquartered in Oman, it is a manufacturing company specializing in the production of photovoltaic and semiconductor grade crystal silicon materials. It has a professional technical and management team. It is committed to the mining and manufacturing of silicon materials in the Middle East, mastering advanced cold hydrogenation and refining, tail gas recovery, reduction, post-processing, electrolytic hydrogen production technology, with a single project annual output of 100,000 tons of high-purity metallurgical silicon.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5437":"Companies in Oman and other Middle East countries initiate internal approval documents, business contract signing, and cooperate with many Chinese mainland enterprises.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5438":"Directly use eSignGlobal SaaS pages, no need for connection, ready to use.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5439":"Unified processing of internal document approval, signing, and management within the company.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5441":"One-click initiation of external commercial cooperation and transaction contracts for global coverage.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5442":"Songliang (iTnio Tech Limited) - International Communications","c2b5f03e-23f6-5443":"The parent company of ITNIO TECH was established in Hong Kong in 2007. Since its inception, it has adhered to the concept of enabling more enterprises to easily connect globally. It has been deeply involved in the international communications field. ITNIO TECH relies on rich industry experience and","c2b5f03e-23f6-5463":"Overseas Joint Signing, Providing a Smoother Collaboration Channel for Pharmaceutical R&D and Testing Services","c2b5f03e-23f6-5464":"Hong Kong Qiyoo Interactive - Gaming Entertainment","c2b5f03e-23f6-5465":"A local Hong Kong gaming entertainment industry company with its own cultural and entertainment platform, widely introducing active creators to provide high-quality, fast-updated game information and entertainment reports to platform users.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5466":"The platform and creators sign the 'Author Contract Agreement', mainly involving Hong Kong corporate entities and individuals.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5467":"Directly use eSignGlobal pages to initiate contract signing.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5468":"Support template setup and customization of signing processes.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5469":"Contract signing and management are completed within the same platform, efficient and quick.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5471":"Shandong Xinglong Yuedong Electronic Technology - Cultural Media","c2b5f03e-23f6-5472":"Mainly engaged in overseas self-media video, creative cooperation, transfer, promotion services. It will distribute the high-quality work resources of overseas bloggers through authorization, purchase, etc., and release them on domestic self-media platforms.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5473":"The main body in China and overseas bloggers sign the 'Copyright License Agreement' to protect the overseas dissemination of the blogger's works and obtain sufficient authorization.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5474":"Helps domestic media enterprises comply with regulations and obtain authorization from overseas individuals for work dissemination.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5475":"Applies to mainland Chinese law, involving individuals in Mexico, France, Thailand, etc.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5476":"Page initiation, both parties sign online.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5477":"Shanghai Prism Pixel - Art Trading","c2b5f03e-23f6-5478":"Mainly engaged in overseas art work distribution and agency services, providing overseas artists, collectors, exhibition institutions, galleries, etc., with overseas agency promotion, operation, and sales services.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5479":"Helps overseas clients achieve the sales and circulation of artworks.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5481":"Helps domestic enterprises comply with regulations and safely cooperate with overseas clients for distribution and agency cooperation.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5482":"Inland initiation, overseas signing, and the signed document can be archived by both parties.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5483":"3-minute online signing, meets the electronic signature legal requirements of both parties' localities.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5111":"Transportation","c2b5f03e-23f6-5112":"New Energy","c2b5f03e-23f6-5113":"International Communications","c2b5f03e-23f6-5114":"Business Going Global","c2b5f03e-23f6-5115":"Medical Services","c2b5f03e-23f6-5116":"Biomedicine","c2b5f03e-23f6-5117":"Game Entertainment","c2b5f03e-23f6-5118":"Cultural Media","c2b5f03e-23f6-5119":"Art Trading","c2b5f03e-23f6-5484":"Shanghai New Vision | Helping overseas human resources service companies recruit suitable talents for going global","c2b5f03e-23f6-5485":"Hong Kong Yutong International | Providing online signature services for large international transport companies for overseas sales contracts","c2b5f03e-23f6-5486":"China Construction | Providing online signature services for large international transport companies for overseas sales contracts","c2b5f03e-23f6-5487":"Fruugo | Ensuring orderly cooperation between overseas platforms and merchants","c2b5f03e-23f6-5488":"United Solar Polysilicon (FZC) - New Energy Materials","c2b5f03e-23f6-5489":"Songliang | Solving the problem of quick signing for Hong Kong enterprises and global partners","c2b5f03e-23f6-5491":"Chuan Yu Interactive | Assisting overseas service providers in compliance and credibility","c2b5f03e-23f6-5492":"Ruipu Gene Technology | Strengthening the authority of medical services through overseas cooperation signing","c2b5f03e-23f6-5493":"Hao Yang Biotechnology | Overseas joint signing provides a smoother cooperation pipeline for pharmaceutical R&D and testing services","c2b5f03e-23f6-5494":"Hong Kong Qiuyou Interactive | Supporting template setup and customization of signing processes","c2b5f03e-23f6-5495":"Shandong Xinglong Yuedong Electronic Technology | Helping domestic media enterprises comply with regulations and obtain authorization from overseas individuals for work dissemination","c2b5f03e-23f6-5496":"Shanghai Prism Pixel | Helping domestic enterprises comply with regulations and securely cooperate with overseas clients for distribution and agency cooperation","c1b5f03e-23f6-549f":"Learn More","b47fde47-0a37-54c2":"eSignGlobal has served over 100 Fortune 500 companies and 200 China Fortune 500 companies, with partners worldwide. The application industries cover Internet+, healthcare, financial technology, B2B e-commerce, and more.","e0c8eb40-407f-c30e":"All Cases","dabb7f78-a569-1df3":"Industry:","f66a83c6-5603-87d3":"Load More...","2b03b002-3be1-bca1":"No More","150b7e67-0ad9-c5f8":"Customer Consultation","6dbabd53-5534-2aa8":"Customer-centric, providing timely response, efficient and professional, comprehensive and detailed services","4e82c6cd-329b-1470":"Consulting Services","e6cf4ebb-a9a9-17fd":"Contact Us","58d269bc-e708-056b":"Follow Us","82db635e-1b8e-7e20":"eSignGlobal  Better Serving Global Customers","a7fee947-1409-05e8":"Try For Free","a2tw42d2-3531-343f":"Contact Sales","3c997ecc-cc63-8200":"Login","0a13faa5-8837-1c03":"International","309b8fca-1503-0aad":"China","2ebc5704-93bc-5d62":"Free Trial - Sign up and go","5dcc0c78-7be5-2a86":"A Leading Global Electronic Signature Service Provider","5fe1eaf9-5923-bdef":"Focused on Document Signature Capabilities, Widely Connected and Integrated, Localized Adaptation","f2ad0830-2783-82f6":"Industry Solutions","4c57f7a5-042a-f864":"Learn More","17d5069a-f116-a8e7":"Products","17d5069a-f116-a8e9":"The main advantage of electronic signatures lies in improving efficiency and convenience, while ensuring the security and compliance of transactions.","17d5069a-f116-a8f2":"eSignGlobal provides efficient, compliant electronic signature services worldwide, helping businesses enhance operational efficiency and competitiveness.","17d5069a-f116-a8f3":"Industries","17d5069a-f116-a8f4":"Finance","17d5069a-f116-a8f5":"Government","17d5069a-f116-a8f6":"Manufacturing","17d5069a-f116-a8f7":"Real Estate","17d5069a-f116-a8f8":"Use Cases","17d5069a-f116-a8f9":"Human Resources","17d5069a-f116-a8g1":"Healthcare","17d5069a-f116-a8g2":"Resources","17d5069a-f116-a8g3":"Learning","17d5069a-f116-a8g4":"Legality Guide","17d5069a-f116-a8g5":"Support","17d5069a-f116-a8g6":"Service Center","17d5069a-f116-a8g7":"Traditional Chinese","17d5069a-f116-a8g8":"Simplified Chinese","17d5069a-f116-a8g9":"English","17d5069a-f116-a8h1":"Sign Contracts with eSignGlobal","17d5069a-f116-a8h2":"Online Signing - Safe and Efficient","17d5069a-f116-a8h3":"eSignature","17d5069a-f116-a8h4":"Daily Sig Volume","17d5069a-f116-a8h5":"Total paid users","17d5069a-f116-a8h6":"Enterprise paid users","17d5069a-f116-a8h7":"Fortune 500 Clients","17d5069a-f116-a8h8":"Ecosystem Partners","17d5069a-f116-a8h9":"Global Signing Support for 100+ Countries and Regions","17d5069a-f116-a8j1":"Market-Leading, Trustworthy","17d5069a-f116-a8j2":"Comprehensive Coverage, Meeting Global Needs","17d5069a-f116-a8j3":"Industry-Leading Security and Top-Tier Service Performance for Customer Business","17d5069a-f116-a8j4":"Global Multi-Data Center","17d5069a-f116-a8j5":"A Wealth of Successful Cases, Rich Experience","17d5069a-f116-a8j6":"In the financial industry, there is a substantial demand for contract signing during the provision of financial services. Increasingly, financial institutions are adopting more efficient signing methods to enhance operational efficiency, reduce costs, and address challenges related to contract creation in the service process.","17d5069a-f116-a8j7":"eSignature for Real Estate","17d5069a-f116-a8j8":"As the industry matures, a concentration effect gradually forms, with the strong becoming stronger. The maturity of the market also means entering a certain bottleneck period. How to achieve cost reduction and efficiency improvement through information technology is a question that many real estate companies need to consider, and electronic contracts are one of the important methods.","17d5069a-f116-a8j9":"Governments are generating a large number of contract signing needs in the process of providing public services. More and more government departments are beginning to introduce more efficient signing methods to improve the efficiency of government services, reduce administrative costs, and solve the problem of contract management during the service process.","17d5069a-f116-a8k1":"eSignature for Manufacturing","17d5069a-f116-a8k2":"Manufacturing companies have formed a certain scale and are mostly group-type companies. They usually have many branches and are widely distributed. Such companies face the challenge of authorizing various branches to issue and use seals due to business needs, and the scenarios involved are very diverse. How to transform from the original offline model to an online model, eSignGlobal provides a mature solution.","17d5069a-f116-a8k3":"Trade","17d5069a-f116-a8k4":"Technology","17d5069a-f116-a8k5":"User Cases","17d5069a-f116-a8k6":"Construction","17d5069a-f116-a8k7":"Software Services","17d5069a-f116-a8k8":"Overseas E-commerce","17d5069a-f116-a8k9":"Customer Service Hotline","17d5069a-f116-a8l1":"Business Cooperation","17d5069a-f116-a8l2":"Year","17d5069a-f116-a8l3":"Million","17d5069a-f116-a1l3":"Thousand","17d5069a-f116-a8l4":"Million","17d5069a-f116-a8l5":"Differences Between Paper Contracts and Electronic Contracts","17d5069a-f116-a8l6":"eIDAS and the Use of Electronic Signatures: A Comparison of Three Levels of Assurance","17d5069a-f116-a8l7":"SES Simple Electronic Signature","17d5069a-f116-a8l8":"Widely used in general signing scenarios","17d5069a-f116-a8l9":"The most basic form of electronic signature, defined as 'electronic data attached to or logically associated with other electronic data and used by the signer for signing'","17d5069a-f116-a9j1":"Used for: daily affairs, signing internal company documents, including emails, low-risk agreements, package delivery terminals","17d5069a-f116-a9j2":"The most basic form of electronic signature, defined as 'electronic data attached to or logically associated with other electronic data and used by the signer for signing'","17d5069a-f116-a9j3":"Compared to advanced electronic signatures, the main drawback of simple electronic signatures is their lower security and authentication. This characteristic makes them more susceptible to forgery and disputes, especially in high-risk transactions or when handling sensitive information","17d5069a-f116-a9j4":"AES Advanced Electronic Signature","17d5069a-f116-a9j5":"Used in scenarios with higher default risk","17d5069a-f116-a9j6":"An advanced electronic signature is one that has the following characteristics: uniquely associated with the signer and capable of identifying the signer; created in a way that allows the signer to retain control; linked to the document in a way that allows detection of any subsequent changes to the data","17d5069a-f116-a9j7":"Used for: financial documents such as financial agreements and bank documents; legally binding documents such as employment contracts and purchase orders","17d5069a-f116-a9j8":"It should be emphasized here that the use of qualified electronic signatures is crucial for ensuring the best security and compliance in scenarios involving strict legal requirements or high-value transactions. Qualified electronic signatures provide a higher level of authentication, legal validity, and protection, and are the preferred choice when legal and financial issues are involved","17d5069a-a116-a9j1":"QES Qualified Electronic Signature","17d5069a-a116-a9j2":"Required for use in specific industries such as government, finance, etc.","17d5069a-a116-a9j3":"A qualified electronic signature is an advanced electronic signature that has the following characteristics: uses a QSCD (Qualified Signature Creation Device). QSCD must comply with strict security technical standards to ensure the highest level of credibility and authenticity in the signature creation process.","17d5069a-a116-a9j4":"Used for: filing patent applications; signing land registry documents; signing business plans; signing legal consent letters, major sales agreements","17d5069a-a116-a9j5":"It should be noted that different levels of electronic signatures may be suitable for different situations, but in the entire European Union, only qualified electronic signatures are explicitly recognized as having the same legal status as handwritten signatures.","17d5069a-a116-a9j6":"The Value of Electronic Signatures in Environmental, Social, and Governance (ESG)","17d5069a-a116-a9j7":"Electronic signatures have significant value in promoting environmental protection, social responsibility, and corporate governance, helping companies achieve sustainable development while also providing convenience and security for individuals and society.","17d5069a-a116-a9j8":"Environmental Protection (Environmental)","17d5069a-a116-a9j9":"Reducing Paper Usage","17d5069a-a116-b9j9":"Reducing Paper Usage","17d5069a-a116-b9j1":"Electronic signatures significantly reduce reliance on paper, helping to reduce deforestation and energy consumption in the paper production process.","17d5069a-a116-b9j2":"Energy Saving","17d5069a-a116-b9j3":"Compared to traditional printing, mailing, faxing, or hand delivery of documents, electronic signatures can significantly reduce transportation and logistics needs, thus saving energy.","17d5069a-a116-b9j4":"Social Responsibility (Social)","17d5069a-a116-b9j5":"Increasing Efficiency","17d5069a-a116-b9j6":"Electronic signatures make contract signing faster and more convenient, especially in cross-regional or multi-party situations, helping to improve work efficiency and promote the development of social productivity.","17d5069a-a116-b9j7":"Portability","17d5069a-a116-b9j8":"Electronic signatures support remote signing, providing convenience for people with limited mobility or those in geographically remote areas, promoting social inclusion and equality.","17d5069a-a116-b9a1":"Corporate Governance (Governance)","17d5069a-a116-b9a2":"Enhancing Security","17d5069a-a116-b9a3":"Electronic signatures combine encryption technology to provide a high level of security, effectively preventing identity fraud and tampering, ensuring the security of transactions.","17d5069a-a116-b9a4":"Increasing Transparency","17d5069a-a116-b9a5":"Electronic signatures record detailed signing processes and timestamps, helping to increase the transparency of contract management, which is particularly important for industries with high audit and compliance requirements.","17d5069a-a116-b9a6":"Promoting Compliance","17d5069a-a116-b9a7":"Electronic signatures comply with the legal and regulatory requirements of many countries and regions, such as the EU's Electronic Identification and Trust Services Regulation (eIDAS) and the U.S. Electronic Signatures in Global and National Commerce Act (ESIGN), helping businesses comply with relevant laws and regulations.","17d5069a-a116-b9a8":"View All  Stories","17d5069a-a116-b9a9":"Reduce costs, enhance legal validity and security, and achieve traceability and environmental friendliness.","17d5069a-a116-a9a1":"Paper contracts are vulnerable to tampering, loss, or damage, which may lead to the loss of important information. As evidence, they may face issues of insufficient effectiveness.","17d5069a-a116-a9a2":"Transactions are faster, more cost-effective, while ensuring the security and compliance of contracts","17d5069a-a116-a9a3":"Simplifies government processes, improves service efficiency and safety","17d5069a-a116-a9a4":"Improves supply chain efficiency, ensures contract security, reduces management costs, and enhances collaborative capabilities","17d5069a-a116-a9a5":"Manufacturing","17d5069a-a116-a9a6":"Simplifies employee onboarding, contract renewal, and offboarding processes, improving the efficiency and compliance of human resources management.","17d5069a-a116-a9a7":"Financial Industry eSignature Solutions","17d5069a-a116-a9a8":"Government Sector eSignature Solutions","c2b5f03e-23f6-5447":"ChuanYu Interactive - Enterprise Overseas Services","c2b5f03e-23f6-5448":"ChuanYu Interactive (Wuhan) Information Technology Co., Ltd. offers integrated solutions for overseas enterprises, with branches in Singapore, Beijing, Wuhan, and Chongqing, providing services in localization, translation, global public opinion monitoring, entertainment, and game translation.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5452":"Overseas individuals verify their identity and sign through email and password.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5454":"RuiPu Genetic Technology - Medical Services","c2b5f03e-23f6-5455":"Hangzhou RuiPu Genetic Technology Co., Ltd. utilizes cutting-edge technology platforms, a leading diverse expert team, and four independently developed core technologies to cover precision diagnostics in oncology, genetic screening in health checks, and large health data management.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5456":"Domestic enterprises initiate the signing of the 'Quality Review Agreement' by overseas individuals to ensure the authority and credibility of test document information and obtain full authorization.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5457":"Domestic enterprises initiate signing through eSignGlobal, and overseas inspectors or experts review medical document information, sign, and complete agreement confirmation after verification.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5458":"Signing through overseas cooperation strengthens the authority of medical services and report security.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5450":"HaoYang Biotechnology - Biopharmaceuticals","c2b5f03e-23f6-5459":"Hangzhou HaoYang Biotechnology Co., Ltd. focuses on providing customers with antibody, fusion protein, and ADC products, offering one-stop research and production services from early drugability evaluation, IND research to commercial production, based in China and serving global clients.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5461":"Domestic enterprises initiate signing of documents such as test reports and authorization letters by overseas individuals for cooperation in gene testing and pharmaceutical development both domestically and abroad.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5462":"Domestic enterprises initiate signing through eSignGlobal, and overseas partners receive the link to the document to be signed via email, authenticating and entering the signing process.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5449":"Domestic enterprises and overseas individuals sign a 'Confidentiality Agreement' for localized operation promotion, translation, and other service cooperation.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5451":"The user's domestic entity initiates the contract signing, and overseas individuals receive the signing notification via email.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5453":"Supporting compliant and trustworthy overseas service cooperation.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5444":"Hong Kong entities are responsible for initiating and managing contract documents, involving application scenarios such as 'Service Cooperation Agreement' and 'Labor Contract'.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5445":"Solves the problem of fast contract signing between Hong Kong companies and global partners.","c2b5f03e-23f6-5446":"On the basis of using the signing package, purchase the eSignGlobal professional edition to lay the foundation for subsequent API service integration and more batch initiation and processing of documents.","17d5069a-a116-a9b1":"Cooperation and Recognition by the China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission (CIETAC)","17d5069a-a116-a9a9":"Privacy Policy","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b1":"Read the story","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b2":"Language","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b3":"Station","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b4":"Product Overview","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b5":"eSignature","c1b5f03e-23f6-54b6":"Why eSignGlobal","17d5069a-a116-a9b2":"Safe and Compliant","17d5069a-a116-a9b3":"Product Function Display","17d5069a-a116-a9b4":"eSignature Security Assurance","17d5069a-a116-a9b5":"eSignGlobal will send the files through a secure channel and Users can choose to add an access password for the invitee to log in before completing the signature.","17d5069a-a116-a9b6":"Signing Behavior Recording","17d5069a-a116-a9b7":"A corresponding certificate of completion will be generated for each signed document, recording the signing behavior of all parties.","17d5069a-a116-a9b8":"Documents Encrypted Storage ","17d5069a-a116-a9b9":"eSignGlobal have a comprehensive security system in place to ensure that signed documents are securely stored and cannot be accessed or extracted by any third party.","17d5069a-a116-a9c1":"Signed Documents Verification ","17d5069a-a116-a9c2":"eSignGlobal completion certificates have been included in the Webtrust trust list. Users can verify via Adobe software.","17d5069a-a116-a9c3":"Available Country/Region List","17d5069a-a116-a9c4":"The legislation of electronic signature varies significantly across countries. Countries/Regions listed above recognize the electronic signature implementation provided by eSignGlobal but the specific limitations were not considered. It is recommended that users need to confirm the specific local regulations before using eSignGlobal eSignature service. For countries and regions not shown in the above table, users may consider agreeing on the dispute jurisdiction to the countries or regions that recognize the eSignature implementation provided by eSignGlobal.","17d5069a-a111-b9a1":"Asia","17d5069a-a111-b9a2":"Europe","17d5069a-a111-b9a3":"North America","17d5069a-a111-b9a4":"South America","17d5069a-a111-b9a5":"Africa","17d5069a-a111-b9a6":"Oceania","17d5069a-a116-a9c5":"Country/Region","17d5069a-a116-a9c6":"Supports or Not","17d5069a-a116-a9c7":"Brunei(Negara Brunei Darussalam)","17d5069a-a116-a9c8":"Hong Kong","17d5069a-a116-a9c9":"India","17d5069a-a116-a9d1":"Indonesia","17d5069a-a116-a9d2":"Israel","17d5069a-a116-a9d3":"Japan","17d5069a-a116-a9d4":"Kazakhstan","17d5069a-a116-a9d5":"Macau","17d5069a-a116-a9d6":"Malaysia","17d5069a-a116-a9d7":"Philippines","17d5069a-a116-a9d8":"Saudi Arabia","17d5069a-a116-a9d9":"Singapore","17d5069a-a116-a9e1":"SouthKorea","17d5069a-a116-a9e2":"SriLanka","17d5069a-a116-a9e3":"Taiwan","17d5069a-a116-a9e4":"Thailand","17d5069a-a116-a9e5":"United Arab Emirates","17d5069a-a116-a9e6":"Vietnam","17d5069a-a116-a9e7":"Austria","17d5069a-a116-a9e8":"Belgium","17d5069a-a116-a9e9":"Czech Republic","17d5069a-a116-a9f1":"Denmark","17d5069a-a116-a9f2":"Estonia","17d5069a-a116-a9f3":"Finland","17d5069a-a116-a9f4":"France","17d5069a-a116-a9f5":"Germany","17d5069a-a116-a9f6":"Greece","17d5069a-a116-a9f7":"Hungary","17d5069a-a116-a1e8":"Iceland","17d5069a-a116-a2e9":"Ireland","17d5069a-a116-a9e0":"Italy","17d5069a-a116-a3f1":"Latvia","17d5069a-a116-a94f2":"Lithuania","17d5069a-a116-a973":"Luxembourg","17d5069a-a116-a984":"Netherlands","17d5069a-a116-a995":"Norway","17d5069a-a116-a1f6":"Poland","17d5069a-a116-a2f7":"Portugal","17d5069a-a116-a3e7":"Romania","17d5069a-a116-a4e8":"Russia","17d5069a-a116-a5e9":"Scotland","17d5069a-a116-a6f1":"Spain","17d5069a-a116-a7f2":"Sweden","17d5069a-a116-a8f3":"Switzerland","17d5069a-a126-a9f4":"Ukraine","17d5069a-a136-a9f5":"United Kingdom","17d5069a-a146-a9f6":"Bermuda","17d5069a-a156-a9f7":"Canada","17d5069a-a166-a9f6":"Guatemala","17d5069a-a176-a9f7":"Mexico","17d5069a-a186-a9f6":"United States","17d5069a-a216-a9f7":"Argentina","17d5069a-a316-a9f7":"Brazil","17d5069a-a416-a9f7":"Chile","17d5069a-a516-a9f7":"Colombia","17d5069a-a616-a9f7":"Ecuador","17d5069a-a716-a9f7":"Peru","17d5069a-a816-a9f7":"Uruguay","17d5061a-a916-a9f7":"Cameroon","17d5062a-a916-a9f7":"Egypt","17d5063a-a916-a9f7":"Nigeria","17d5064a-a116-a9f7":"South Africa","17d5065a-a116-a9f7":"Australia","18d5069a-a116-a9a0":"Dispute Resolution Guidance","18d5069a-a116-a9a1":"Choose an appropriate arbitration commission","18d5069a-a116-a9a2":"To avoid disputes, eSignGlobal recommend that users may choose an appropriate national/ regional arbitration committee to handle potential disputes while signing a contract. This may enhance the legal validity of usersr electronic signature. The following aspects shall be take into consideration when selecting the arbitration committee:","18d5069a-a116-a9a3":"The electronic signature implementation provided by eSignGlobal be recognized by local law.","18d5069a-a116-a9a4":"The signed document content be recognized by local law.","18d5069a-a116-a9a5":"No other legal prohibitive provisions. ","18d5069a-a116-a9a6":"Reference arbitration clause available","18d5069a-a116-a9a7":"The following listed arbitration committees and stipulated arbitration clauses are provided for your reference:","18d5069a-a116-a9b1":"China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission（CIETAC）","18d5069a-a116-a9b2":"The China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission (CIETAC) is one of the major permanent arbitration institutions in the world.","18d5069a-a116-a9b3":"CIETAC Model Clause：","18d5069a-a116-a9b4":"-Any dispute arising from or in connection with this Contract shall be submitted to China International Economic and Trade Arbitration Commission (CIETAC) for arbitration which shall be conducted in accordance with the CIETAC's arbitration rules in effect at the time of applying for arbitration.The arbitral award is final and binding upon both parties.","18d5069a-a116-a9b5":"-All disputes arising from or related to this contract shall be governed by the laws of Hong Kong.","18d5069a-a116-a9b6":"Users may refer to the following links for further guidance:","18d5069a-a116-a9b7":"Hong Kong International Arbitration Centre（HKIAC）","18d5069a-a116-a9b8":"The Hong Kong International Arbitration Centre (HKIAC) is one of the world's leading dispute resolution institutions, specializing in arbitration, mediation, conciliation, and domain name dispute resolution.","18d5069a-a116-a9b9":"HKIAC Model Clauses","18d5069a-a116-a9c1":"Any dispute, controversy, difference or claim arising out of or relating to this contract, including the existence, validity, interpretation, performance, breach or termination thereof or any dispute regarding non- contractual obligations arising out of or relating to it shall be referred to and finally resolved by arbitration administered by the Hong Kong International Arbitration Centre (HKIAC) under the HKIAC Administered Arbitration Rules in force when the Notice of Arbitration is submitted. The law of this arbitration clause shall be ... (Hong Kong law). ","18d5069a-a116-a9c2":"Users may refer to the following links for further guidance:","18d5069a-a116-a9c3":"Singapore International Arbitration Centre（SIAC）","18d5069a-a116-a9c4":"SIAC is a global arbitral institution providing cost-competitive and efficient case management services to parties from all over the world.","18d5069a-a116-a9c5":"SIAC Model Clause","18d5069a-a116-a9c6":"-Any dispute arising out of or in connection with this contract, including any question regarding its existence, validity or termination, shall be referred to and finally resolved by arbitration administered by the Singapore International Arbitration Centre (“SIAC”) in accordance with the Arbitration Rules of the Singapore International Arbitration Centre (“SIAC Rules”) for the time being in force, which rules are deemed to be incorporated by reference in this clause.-The seat of the arbitration shall be [Singapore].*\n-This contract is governed by the laws of _________________.","18d5069a-a116-a9c7":"Users may refer to the following links for further guidance:","18d5069a-a116-a9c8":"Declaration","18d5069a-a116-a9c9":"Due to the differences in national legislation,the information provided on this page or any other guidance or instructions that may be provided on this website are for reference only. eSignGlobal recommend that users need to confirm the specific local regulations or seek the guidance of a professional attorney before using eSignGlobal eSignature service.","60ad78ff-bc2e-1c2e":"Privacy Notice","a14b4775-1c58-97e7":"Please choose whether to accept or not","45661b73-ddd7-0818":"We use cookies to provide our service, improve security, personalize the user experience, analyze performance and trafic on our website.Click","4f00e1c3-856e-0ef2":"here","cfcb607d-b39a-f43e":"to read our Privacy Policy. You can manage your selection by clicking “Manage Cookie”.","1fa624ce-6920-acfb":"Manage Cookie","06b5429e-d43e-01c9":"Accept","9bb49bf9-97a6-ce02":"Manage cookie preferences","04ddeb5f-25dc-84ce":"When you visit our website, we store cookies on your browser to collect information. The information collected might relate to you,your preferences or your device, and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to and to provide a more personalized webexperience. However, you can choose not to allow certain types of cookies, which may impact your experience of the site and the serviceswe are able to offer. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings according to yourpreference. You cannot opt-out of our Required Cookies as they are deployed in order to ensure the proper functioning of our website (such as prompting the cookie banner and remembering your settings, to log into your account, to redirect you when you log out, etc.).Click","29e2a92c-a6d8-a72f":"here","7689f68b-cce1-6bbe":"to learn more information about the Cookies used.","901a1e4d-2d6c-45a5":"Required Cookie","35dc5176-6c17-80b9":"We use required cookies to perform essential website functions. For example, they're used to log you in, save your language preferences,improve performance, route traffic between web servers, detect the size of your screen, determine page load times, improve userexperience, and for audience measurement. These cookies are necessary for our websites to work.","f18767e0-85a8-5ef2":"Accept","6885f625-fc39-2efc":"Analytics Cookie","e3c9404a-93c6-ccc7":"We allow third parties to use analytics cookies to understand how you use our websites so we can make them better. For example, they're used to gather information about the pages you visit and how many clicks you need to accomplish a task.","628bbcae-3301-8cac":"Accept","c6f800f7-ebce-19ed":"Reject","ae521e26-6988-e2a8":"Save","aeg21e26-6988-e2a8":"Manage Cookie","8a2f0767-ed5d-a406":'How to login eSignGlobal with "iAM Smart" and Initiate Signing',"6f659706-299e-b52f":"About eSignGlobal","97b03e0e-a660-2e6a":"News details","bba595b4-5dc5-52fa":'Recently, eSignGlobal, a product provided by ESIGN HK, has officially integrated with "iAM Smart", a one-stop personalized digital service platform. This integration allows users to perform effective identity verification through "iAM Smart", thereby enabling them to use eSignGlobal’s higher security level e-signature services with greater peace of mind. Both individuals and businesses can initiate signing processes, with the entire signing procedure traceable, ensuring maximum security of user data and full compliance throughout.',"823aac5c-79e4-ed94":'The collaboration between eSignGlobal and "iAM Smart" will advance the electronic signature application market in Hong Kong by providing online identity confirmation for signatories. This addresses the issue of unclear signatory identities present in traditional email-based signing methods and enables broader application in various document types, such as labor contracts, business agreements, and financial documents. Currently, eSignGlobal is one of the few electronic signature providers in Hong Kong with data centers and service capabilities localized in the region, meeting the needs of businesses, and individuals through localized product adaptations.',"e8e3b96f-431c-ad99":"Additionally, eSignGlobal actively practices ESG principles by helping businesses save on logistics and labor costs, reducing paper and energy consumption, and promoting green signing. Moving forward, eSignGlobal will continue to adhere to its principle of 'making signing more convenient and trust simpler' by offering innovative products that cater to Hong Kong’s technological and innovative development needs.","1d25391c-2ce6-a521":'A user can easily login eSignGlobal with "iAM Smart" and initiate electronic signatures to enjoy a secure, efficient, and eco-friendly signing experience:',"aa56c3ab-c2d9-9063":'1.Click "Login with iAM Smart" in eSignGlobal website. Open the "iAM Smart" mobile app, click "Scan" button to scan the "iAM Smart" QR code for authorising the login authentication to eSignGlobal.',"d7a40de6-8822-c793":'2.If this is your first time to login  "iAM Smart", eSignGlobal will request your personal data from "iAM Smart" for account opening. Click the "Personal Data from iAM Smart" button, open the "iAM Smart" mobile app on your phone, click "To fill" and authorise your personal information to eSignGlobal. After that, you may confirm the personal information in eSignGlobal.',"f26e61f6-ba8f-d697":'3. After confirming your information, enter the verification code, click the "Submit" button, your account will be linked up with "iAM Smart".  You may proceed to the signing page. Once signing is complete, click "Finish" to end the process.',"09836505-7c95-bf91":"eSignGlobal specializes in electronic signature services, providing secure and reliable identity verification, e-signatures, electronic contracts, smart fulfillment, and legal services to government entities, businesses, and individual users. With industry-leading technological strength, eSignGlobal offers software applications and technical support featuring top-notch data security and privacy protection mechanisms, as well as advanced AI applications. eSignGlobal’s products are widely used across various industries including Internet+ governance, healthcare, fintech, international trade, logistics, tourism, and human resources. To date, eSignGlobal has served over 1 million businesses and more than 100 million individual users.","806f964d-d59b-cc47":'eSignGlobal Becomes the First E-Signature SaaS Service to Integrate with "iAM Smart"',"15737fee-dd7d-577f":"Connect Us","c99086f0-a130-661b":"Global signing without distance, just trust and ease","9b9a8a80-6f06-4349":"First Name","0975c730-554b-bba5":"Please enter your first name","ffdef2cf-b256-2c78":"Last Name","5fc3e67e-8636-9d78":"Please enter your last name","c49d2971-5aaa-f913":"Phone Number","5c052fa6-4acc-731d":"Region","5586e1b5-98f7-96b4":"Please enter your phone number","505d5bfe-47c8-5821":"Company","5f101935-a6d4-6e90":"Please enter your company","d37fb373-6a84-a838":"Email","c1892060-a6c8-a5c8":"Please enter your  email","60fa85e0-0e20-9d57":"Country/region","bcb2a0bf-0806-b4c5":"Please enter where your business is registered","8aba431e-08d8-ad2c":"What are you interested in?","3fhdds3d-d5hs-jdh7":"（optional）","f5a971c6-6298-8ecb":"Please enter what are you interested in","9c348222-75ea-4544":"I confirm that I have read and agree to the use of my data in accordance with the ","e66b6a50-e256-9def":"eSignGlobal Privacy Policy","d5c13259-7bfd-0f61":".","7d33d037-1204-8439":"Submit","a1b2c3d4-e5f6-a7b8":"Name","b2c3d4e5-f6a7-b8c9":"What are you interested in? (optional)","c3d4e5f6-a7b8-c9d0":"Clicking “Submit” means you have read and agree to the use of my data in accordance with the eSignGlobal Privacy Policy.","9c01fdcc-cff7-45bc":"Thanks!","cb3cef22-28dd-f709":"We will contact you on the next working day.","7bd0c856-4fa3-5fba":"Please be sure to answer calls from numbers starting with (852) .","94b54f97-52b3-6b98":"Speak to our electronic signature experts for：","8acded62-15e1-8c56":"Product demos","c1b53f08-8007-427a":"Personalised solutions for electronic signature","d94976c4-ed1a-642c":"Pricing","e53a64ef-44d4-3ed0":"Integration support","a9f73eee-93d6-acf0":"We can offer you：","b4e6603e-50e3-fe0f":"Global electronic signature service solutions","5fde11ef-28c5-bc0b":"Industry’s strongest security system, top-notch service performance","b75d3e71-f855-ca6e":"Global multi-data center, meeting data compliance requi